Rodgers has remained cryptic about his long-term plans with the Jets, saying that any decisions will be made in consultation with Jets owner Woody Johnson. Rodgers has also expressed his frustration with leaks within the team, suggesting that they will make it harder for the Jets to win. Despite the uncertainty surrounding his future, Rodgers has agreed to take a pay cut to remain with the Jets.

summary: In 2024, Hanukkah will commence on Christmas Day, marking a rare occurrence. The Jewish holiday will be widely celebrated with traditional rituals, including the lighting of the menorah, as seen in the PBS NewsHour report. "Hanukkah Lights 2024" highlights the importance of the holiday within the Jewish community. For some families, the overlap with Christmas has led to the creation of "Chrismukkah," a blend of both celebrations (The New York Times). name: Norovirus
summary: Norovirus cases have been rapidly increasing in the United States, particularly during this winter season. According to data from the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC), there has been a significant surge in reported cases. This highly contagious stomach bug, also known as the "stomach flu," causes severe symptoms such as vomiting, diarrhea, and abdominal pain.
